{
  "doc_id": "6968",
  "text": "Note that some of these results were already presented in a briefer work [CITATION_1] ; significantly, we here offer convincing evidence (Section V) to support the conjecture made there on the local structure of current fluctuations. In addition, we present a new extension to the triangular lattice (Section IV) and provide many previously unpublished calculational details including a more explicit derivation of the AFR than the one shown in [CITATION_2] (Appendix A) as well as the corresponding macroscopic optimization argument for the 2-d ZRP with non-decreasing interactions (Appendix C).",
