      "span_text": "In addition, we present a new extension to the triangular lattice (Section IV) and provide many previously unpublished calculational details including a more explicit derivation of the AFR than the one shown in [CITATION_2] (Appendix A) as well as the corresponding macroscopic optimization argument for the 2-d ZRP with non-decreasing interactions (Appendix C)."
